$ npm install -g express-generator
g for global install

$ express exp2015 --hogan -c less
hoogan for hogan templating (which is esentially moustache)
c for CSS
less for less (can also choose stylus but NOT SAAS)

$ cd exp2015

$ npm install (for dependencies... will also install express and everything required from your package.json file)

$ DEBUG=exp2015:* npm start
exp2015 from bin/www line 8

$ npm install -g nodemon
nodemon keeps track of changes in files and automatically restarts the server for us on every file save

$ nodemon bin/www
runs server with nodemon

